The paper deals with the design of precoders in a distributed network MIMO system, where each transmitter has only local channel state information. This falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the impact of imperfect channel state information (cs.SI) and proposes a new transmission scheme to improve the degrees of freedom (cs.MM). Finally, the paper considers the optimality of the proposed scheme (cs.SY).
